Zahra Ouaziz (Arabic) (amụrụ na Disemba 20, na afọ 1969 na Oulmes) bụ onye Morocco na-agba ọsọ ogologo oge lara ezumike nká
Ọ bụ onye na-edekọ ihe ndekọ Afrịka na mita 3000 na mita 5000.
Ouaziz mebiri ihe ndekọ Africa nke mita 5000 na afọ 1998, n'oge 14:40.19
Leah Malot nke Kenya meriri ndekọ ahụ na Septemba, na afọ 2000, ndekọ ọhụrụ ahụ bụ 14:39.83.
Ouaziz chọtara ọtụtụ ihe ịga nke ọma ya n'okporo ụzọ ahụ, mana o nwetakwara ọlaọcha abụọ na IAAF World Cross Country Championships ma bụrụ onye mmeri nke afọ 1999 Cross Internacional de Itálica.
